name: Allianceauth
body:
### Eve Alliance Auth
The AllianceAuth is a Django application designed to help eve online alliances quickly and effectively manage their users and applications.

### Quick Checkout
```
$ git clone https://github.com/R4stl1n/allianceauth.git
$ cd allianceauth
```

### Authors and Contributors
